Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.88,0:00:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸中的鼓动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.92,0:00:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你延续而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.88,0:00:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.92,0:00:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使受了伤也无妨  不转移目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.92,0:00:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想热切、激烈地生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.92,0:00:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我永不放弃的坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.92,0:00:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想紧紧抱着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.92,0:00:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去或痛楚都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.92,0:01:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引导至鲜明的、一瞬间的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.92,0:01:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸中的鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.92,0:01:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你延续而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.63,0:01:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不是战斗的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.83,0:01:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续留在这艘舰里会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.83,0:01:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔‧拉巴伯‧温拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.77,0:01:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是钢弹驾驶员中最错误的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十八话\N[朝混沌出击]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滚开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄准不好啊，我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去，有一个时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以一个按钮\N决定所有战斗的胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种讨厌的精神的根源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这种叫MD的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而它们的代表就是那艘天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果从战争里\N失去[人]这特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胜利和败北也是悲惨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.19,0:03:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神不会向任何一方伸出祂的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要说漂亮话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你，战火扩散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.24,0:03:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的对手应该只有我就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做好心理准备了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，但我今次不会留手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直以来多次反抗死的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次我也要反抗它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.49,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你们有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.66,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先带我们去万年和平号吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去万年和平号?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.63,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去杰克斯就会如愿以偿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要进入万年和平号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.61,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改变天秤座的轨道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯的意图…难道…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.22,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，他的目标是终结地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何要阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样，我们的赎罪就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,计算出冲入大气层的地点了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据现在的情况推测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座能冲入地球大气层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撞落北半球大陆的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是69%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时释放出来的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推测大约有6千兆吨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那样，米利亚尔特司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坎斯，万年和平号和天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若这两艘战舰\N撞落那个蔚蓝的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,季节就会停顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漫长的冬天就会来临吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是在万年和平号的推进系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.07,0:05:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坏掉的前提下计算出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.24,0:05:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万年和平号是我过去的战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它会理解我的意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.68,0:05:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹们真的会让你做吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.75,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.29,0:05:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们当然会挡在我面前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在等他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和历史的必然推展或大义不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是名为战斗专家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等! 希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何一定要出击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座会毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经没有任何战斗的理由了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王兄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特和白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,输了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯…并不认为输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，杰克斯和特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.78,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来也无意结束这场战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说如果你出战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战争就会结束吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会打倒杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着是特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样，战争就会结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，如果你活下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平就会来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我唯一能为你做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾答应你 我会保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保护你和这个地球圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有战斗一途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.56,0:07:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行! 不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你打算去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.68,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这房间…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的控制室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有装了零式系统的气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和零式系统有直接联系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的战斗意思驱使所有MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔‧温拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我决斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在零式系统之间的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我输了给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.89,0:09:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，今次会有何结果呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.32,0:09:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为能凭自己的意思战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的话，我不想战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果不那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们就不会投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争也不会结束  对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，零式系统和血肉之驱的意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来分出哪一方优胜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我拒绝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何执着于战争?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不惜这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仁慈的卡特尔小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了亲人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了不令大家伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只好战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.97,0:09:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的爸爸为了\N不令我伤心而战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要美丽地战斗后而死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你也憎恨战争吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.79,0:10:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!破坏和杀戮\N并非战争的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.33,0:10:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要打倒的敌人\N在我们心里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.83,0:10:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信凌驾战争的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信渴望和平的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你说你一直为了大家在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.57,0:10:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但大家有为你做过什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.61,0:10:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我战斗并非为了要别人报答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，你是小朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别再打…桃乐丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星出卖了钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的居民杀了你的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，武装起来的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么也不理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就向地球宣布要独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.08,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直以来的战斗\N全是白费啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关怀别人的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过份关怀的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这种最坏的事态啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体上船了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.63,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，就此飞向MO-II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.24,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再呼唤会妨碍他们战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但希洛打算去死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，我求你，请答话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生命不值钱，特别是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等我，卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.09,0:12:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，对不起\N我有俗务要办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.86,0:12:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能再帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别介意，够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一样，迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做好心理准备了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去到万年和平号的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.21,0:13:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有我们其中之一就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使有人被抛开\N你也别介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我没那种时间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有想穿越这种地方的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.11,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的不该找到他们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神和瘟神要过去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚…什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我们的力量不能令宇宙统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但地球却逐渐统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那位小姐的力量吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兄弟们 在和卡特尔少爷见面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也不准死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不出真功夫吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是，你不能吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我不会留手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.63,0:14:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种纯真 那种幼智 那种仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会令你们战败啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只懂以这方式战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，因为这样不停战败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.98,0:15:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的人\N才不用被卷入战火之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就毫无改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，怎么办才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为卫星的领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堂堂正正挑起战争就行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像米利亚尔特大人那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝，你错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.83,0:15:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，应该让全人类看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令他们不想再看见战争的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.50,0:15:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲惨战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是这场战争的意义吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了令战争\N从人类的历史里消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.71,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是没收武器不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不令人类的心改革…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不那样做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.49,0:15:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类…就会像父亲大人那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你比我更仁慈呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那样说，我也不会高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.73,0:16:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仁慈是活下去的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽了力才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就最适合人类啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.27,0:16:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝…你和从前的我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太憎恨战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.28,0:16:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能信赖自己的仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.12,0:16:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…不可否定仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.62,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我给特洛瓦教懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.56,0:16:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们非接受一切不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.13,0:16:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类需要那种仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类就没有存在意义啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.11,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,单纯只是活下去的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.38,0:16:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是…不会关怀任何人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.75,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连动物也不如的…种族啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.96,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?为何不用那条龙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.47,0:17:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和你堂堂正正决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不像你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你犹疑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.07,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你当时为何不杀我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.34,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能杀死\N寥寥可数理解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不要犹疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.50,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是个只懂那样蔑视别人的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗时始终只懂胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道多少人\N为了你而死吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.98,0:17:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,截至昨日合共99，822人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，今日战死的有多少人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在确定了的有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.62,0:18:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙82人，我军105人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待会把名字告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了战斗而牺牲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.04,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我全都记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺边塔、赛普提姆、班迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.64,0:18:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安、华卡、奥图、本度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是不能忘怀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.42,0:18:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对死者只能表示哀悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.09,0:18:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我希望你也明白这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.53,0:18:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们绝对不是白死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.74,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起…五飞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯? 你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飞…我永远的好友啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和你们战斗令我觉得自豪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.79,0:19:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…这种结果…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会承认啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.83,0:19:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特…我先行一步了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.91,0:19:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.31,0:19:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次赢了…\N今次就不和我再战吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，请下命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.59,0:19:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们世界国家军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.33,0:19:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在宣布战败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.07,0:19:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特…特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种羞耻的宣言不要我重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点通报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.11,0:20:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真伟大，特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.98,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你在那里吗? 桃乐丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才，地球方面\N发出战败宣言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战败宣言?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.09,0:20:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，索敌队说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达已经战死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那种事…不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们胜利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.17,0:20:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.31,0:20:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会中止把这艘舰撞落地球
