Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，没办法把这件事告诉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去希洛那里吧
